Bunny Up

Create an app that will choose random groups for the class.

Take a list of student names, and the desired group size as input, and print out a list of the assigned groups.

  students = (Iwona, Craig, GraemeK, Kathryn, Kieran, Peter, Ere, Chae, Zsolt, Simon, Syed, Kieran, GraemeS, Keith, Nevin)
Things to think about

What to do if the class does not divide evenly into the group size?

you need to decide what to do with the remaining students
how do you ensure the list is randomised